name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On November 11, "Changzhou Huali" announced that its chairman Cheng Yong was coerced into admitting that he was involved in accepting 8 million deposits and cash bribes, and he jumped off the building unjustly. In his suicide note, Cheng Yong said that he was interviewed by the Municipal Commission for Discipline Inspection and was involved in the loan issue of the deputy district mayor. At first, he just wanted to pay the money and leave as soon as possible, but he didn't expect to be caught in a dilemma. It's a bit hard in there, and the days are like years. All the evidence is a coincidence that happened to be guessed. I don't want to suffer anymore. Bye!

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On November 11, employees and family members of Changzhou Huali went to the Changzhou Municipal Government Building to seek justice for their chairman who had jumped from the building.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On November 11, the Science People WeChat public account published an article directly pointing out that Professor Su Shicheng and Academician Song Erwei of Zhongshan Second Hospital were suspected of academic misconduct.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
On November 10, three months after the flood in Zhuozhou, Xi Jinping went to Zhuozhou for inspection.
"I just miss it, so I came to take a look."

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On November 11, as the incident of Lujiazui suing Sugang for 10 billion yuan in compensation for toxic land was exposed, some owners went to the property and held up banners demanding that Lujiazui return their homes.
